<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Contact Support - Bamboo Shop</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f6f9fc; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    h2 { color: #2b7a0b; }
    .reply-box { background-color: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #2b7a0b; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; font-style: italic; }
    .original-message { font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 10px; }
    p { margin: 10px 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>Thank you for reaching out to Bamboo Shop. Regarding your message about <strong>"{{subject}}"</strong>, our team has a response for you:</p>

    <div class="reply-box">
      {{replyContent}}
    </div>

    <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to contact us or visit our shop.</p>

    <div class="original-message">
      <strong>Your Original Message:</strong><br/>
      {{originalMessage}}
    </div>

    <p>Best regards,<br/>Bamboo Shop Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>